'''兒童文學遺產獎''' （前身為'''蘿拉·英格斯·懷德獎'''，2018年起變更為此名）是一項由美國兒童圖書館服務協會 (ALSC)所頒發的獎項，頒發給在美國兒童文學上長期耕耘、並為兒童文學帶來巨大且永久貢獻的作家或插畫家。<ref name=AboutWilder/> 獎項以第一位得獎者——[[蘿拉·英格斯·懷德|蘿拉·英格斯·懷德]]的名字命名。<ref name=AboutWilder />

==更名原因==
2018年2月，承辦獎項頒發的兒童圖書館服務協會(ALSC)宣布成立了一個專案小組，重新審查該獎項名稱是否恰當，小組成員亦包含了美國印地安圖書館協會(AILA)的代表。<ref name="ALSC Announcement">{{cite web|last1=Lindsay|first1=Nina|title=ALSC Awards Program Review Update|url=http://www.alsc.ala.org/blog/2018/03/alsc-awards-program-review-update/|website=ALSC Blog|publisher=ALA|accessdate=27 March 2018|archive-date=2020-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200919002245/https://www.alsc.ala.org/blog/2018/03/alsc-awards-program-review-update/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之所以召開本次行動，是因為外界批評了懷德在書中對原住民與非裔美國人有不當描述。<ref>{{cite web|last1=Reese|first1=Debbie|title=BIG NEWS: A possible change in name of ALA's Laura Ingalls Wilder Award!|url=https://americanindiansinchildrensliterature.blogspot.com/2018/02/big-news-possible-change-in-name-of.html|website=American Indians in Children's Literature|accessdate=27 March 2018|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022004725/https://americanindiansinchildrensliterature.blogspot.com/2018/02/big-news-possible-change-in-name-of.html|dead-url=no}}</ref> 重新命名的建議在2018年6月23日被提出。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.ala.org/alsc/awardsgrants/bookmedia/wildermedal/wilderabout|title=About the Children's Literature Legacy Award|last=admin|date=1999-11-30|work=Association for Library Service to Children (ALSC)|access-date=2018-06-24|language=en|archive-date=2016-04-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160421125422/http://www.ala.org/alsc/awardsgrants/bookmedia/wildermedal/wilderabout|dead-url=no}}</ref> 

ALSC委員會發現懷德的作品「含有刻板印象的描述，與ALSC的『包容、正直、尊重、熱忱』核心價值並不一致」。<ref name=Lou>{{cite web |url=https://www.yahoo.com/news/laura-ingalls-wilder-apos-name-181423728.html |title=Laura Ingalls Wilder's Name Cut From Award For Her 'Stereotypical' Depictions |work=HuffPost |via=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] |author=Michelle Lou |date=June 25, 2018 |accessdate=June 26, 2018 |archive-date=2018-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180627034557/https://www.yahoo.com/news/laura-ingalls-wilder-apos-name-181423728.html |dead-url=no }}</ref> ALSC認為懷德的描寫對少數族群，特別是美國原住民構成了種族歧視。<ref name=Lou/>該獎項被正式更名為「兒童文學遺產獎」。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://apnews.com/19112531f7a24c9c8ab43b7968c96a1d|title=Association removes Laura Ingalls Wilder's name from award|date=2018-06-24|website=AP NEWS|access-date=2019-01-15|archive-date=2020-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200819205456/https://apnews.com/19112531f7a24c9c8ab43b7968c96a1d|dead-url=no}}</ref>

